162 hundred dollars of the fee in the state lottery fund. The
163 remaining eight hundred dollars of such fee shall not be
164 considered state revenues and shall be paid as follows:
165 (a) One hundred dollars shall be transmitted to the
166 Missouri state highway patrol for use in investigations and
167 enforcement of sections 313.425 to 313.437;
168 (b) One hundred dollars shall be transmitted to the
169 Missouri attorney general's office for use in illegal
